name: MONEROCARD - 2016 NFT - Age of Chains, Series 1
description:
1 MONEROCARD from Age of Chains from the year 2016. Age of Chains was one of the worlds most early NFT-Projects and started its Card selling at the Counterparty Blockchain. Their art speaks for itself. This is the Card Number 003 from Series 1 with current 862 Cards minted.
